text: Tele Quisqueya (TQ) is a television station located in Saint-Marc, Haiti. Broadcasting on channel 15 UHF and channel 9 VHF, it covers all of Artibonite and other departments in the country. As a commercial station it offers a dynamic program with rich content. The station also operates an FM radio station ("amazone") on 99.1 FM. ==External links == * TQ's official website Category:Television stations in Haiti
title: Tele Quisqueya
